PK — ab Observer Pattern ko bhi “feel aaya” mode me crystal clear karte hain 🔥
Ye pattern interview + real systems (Kafka, events, notifications) me bahut use hota hai.

🧠 1️⃣ Observer Pattern kya hai (1 line)
Ek object change hota hai → sabko automatically bata deta hai
🧠 Aha
1 → many notification system
🎯 2️⃣ Real Life Feel
📱 Instagram Example
User (Publisher)
   ↓ post dala
Followers (Observers)
   ↓
Notification mil gaya 🔔
🌦️ Weather App
Weather Station → change
TV / Mobile → update
🧠 Aha
Observer = subscriber
Observable = publisher
⚙️ 3️⃣ Core Components
🟢 Observable (Publisher)
Data hold karta hai
Observers list maintain karta hai
Notify karta hai
🔵 Observer (Subscriber)
Update receive karta hai
Apna logic chalata hai
🧠 Flow
State change → notify → update()
🔥 4️⃣ Full Flow (Simple)
1. Observer subscribe karta hai
2. Publisher state change karta hai
3. Publisher notify karta hai
4. Observer update handle karta hai
💡 5️⃣ Push vs Pull (MOST IMPORTANT 🔥)
🟢 1. Push Model
💡 Meaning
Publisher → data push karega
Flow
Publisher → update(data)
Example
WeatherStation → temperature, humidity bhej diya
🧠 Aha
Publisher decide karega kya bhejna hai
👍 Pros
Simple
Fast
👎 Cons
Extra data bhi bhej sakta hai
🔵 2. Pull Model
💡 Meaning
Observer → data khud fetch karega
Flow
Publisher → update()
Observer → getData()
Example
Observer → "kya change hua?"
🧠 Aha
Observer control me hai
👍 Pros
Flexible
Only required data fetch
👎 Cons
Extra calls
⚔️ Push vs Pull (Comparison)
Push → "ye lo data"
Pull → "mujhe data chahiye"
🧠 Final Aha
Push = eager
Pull = lazy
⚙️ 6️⃣ Code Level Thinking
🟢 Observable
addObserver()
removeObserver()
notifyObservers()
🔵 Observer
update()
🔥 Key Line
notifyObservers() → sabka update() call hota hai
💥 7️⃣ Real System Mapping
Kafka / Event Driven
Producer → event publish
Consumers → receive event

👉 Same Observer pattern 🔥

Microservices
Order Service → event
Notification Service → observe
🚨 8️⃣ Common Mistakes
❌ 1. Tight coupling
Direct calls → avoid
❌ 2. No unsubscribe
Memory leak 💥
❌ 3. Too many observers
Performance issue
🧠 9️⃣ Interview Killer Lines
Observer pattern provides loose coupling between publisher and subscribers.
It is widely used in event-driven and reactive systems.
🔥 🔟 One Line Summary
Observer Pattern = state change → automatic notification to subscribers
🧠 Ultimate Aha
Instead of asking → system khud bata deta hai